  <official_title>Evaluation of the Safety of Primaquine in Combination With Artemether-lumefantrine in Glucose-6-phosphate Dehydrogynase Deficient Males With an Asymptomatic Malaria Infection in Burkina Faso (SAFEPRIM)</official_title>
