  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the tolerability and safety of increasing doses of
      primaquine in combination with artemether-lumefantrine in G6PD deficient males with an
      asymptomatic P. falciparum malaria infection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
